---
import ContactPanel from './ContactPanel.astro';
---

<div class="sidebar-widget">
  <div class="sidebar-section-header">
    <span class="sidebar-section-title">聯絡我們</span>
  </div>

  <button
    type="button"
    data-contact-open
    class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-blue-accent px-5 py-2.5 text-[14px] font-semibold text-white transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-blue-brand"
  >
    <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
      <path
        stroke-linecap="round"
        stroke-linejoin="round"
        stroke-width="2"
        d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"
      />
    </svg>
    聯絡我們
  </button>

  <p class="mt-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-ink-soft">
    想知道什麼遊輪資訊，對於網站有什麼指教，都請不吝告訴我
  </p>
</div>

<ContactPanel />
